<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>WiseLedger Landing Page</title>

  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <!--Library AOS-->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/aos@next/dist/aos.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/dist/index.css" />
</head>

<body>
  <div id="hero-page">
    <header class="hero-header" style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;">
      <a href="#" class="logo-text">
        <img src="/assets/image/logo.png" alt="WiseLedger Logo" style="height: 45px; width: auto; object-fit: contain;">
      </a>
      <div>
        <a href="login" class="btn-custom-outline">Sign in</a>
        <a href="register" class="btn-custom-solid">Sign up</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container hero-section">
      <div class="row align-items-center w-100">
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
          <h1 class="hero-title">
            Manage Your<br />
            Money Smarter<br />
            with <span class="text-brand">WiseLedger</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle">
            Plan your monthly budget, track daily expenses, and reflect on
            your spending habits in one simple platform designed for smarter
            financial decisions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
          <div class="hero-image-container">
            <div class="hero-image-bg"></div>
            <img src="/assets/image/Mascott2x.png" alt="WiseLedger Mascot" class="hero-image" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <footer class="footer-bar"></footer>
  </div>

  <!--Navbar-->
  <nav id="sticky-nav" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000">
    <a class="nav-logo" href="#" style="text-decoration: none;">
      <span>Wise<em>Ledger</em></span>
    </a>

    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#hero-page">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="#about-section" class="active">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Lorem</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Lorem</a></li>
    </ul>

    <div class="nav-cta">
      <a href="login" class="btn-outline">Sign In</a>
      <a href="register" class="btn-solid">Sign Up</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!--ABOUT / MISSION SECTION-->
  <section id="about-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="tag-pill">Tentang Kami</div>
        <h2 style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Tiga Layana Utama WiseLedger</h2>
        <p>
          Setiap fitur dirancang untuk membangun kebiasaan finansial yang
          sehat, sadar, dan berkelanjutan.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mission-grid">
        <div class="mission-card reveal" data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-delay="100" data-aos-duration="300">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 26 26" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <rect x="4" y="2" width="14" height="22" rx="3" fill="#2F4F7F" opacity="0.12" />
              <rect x="4" y="2" width="14" height="22" rx="3" stroke="#2F4F7F" stroke-width="1.6" />
              <path d="M8 8h6M8 12h6M8 16h4" stroke="#2F4F7F" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" />
              <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="5" fill="#D4A437" />
              <path d="M17.5 20l1.5 1.5 3-3" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Financial Discipline</h3>
          <p>
            Membantu pengguna membangun disiplin finansial melalui pencatatan
            rutin yang sederhana dan terstruktur setiap harinya.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mission-card" data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-delay="100" data-aos-duration="600">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 26 26" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle cx="13" cy="13" r="10" stroke="#2F4F7F" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" />
              <path d="M13 7v6l4 4" stroke="#D4A437" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round" />
              <circle cx="13" cy="13" r="2" fill="#2F4F7F" />
              <path d="M7 4.5C8.8 3.2 11 2.5 13 2.5" stroke="#D4A437" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Kakeibo Reflection</h3>
          <p>
            Mengadaptasi metode Kakeibo untuk mendorong refleksi bulanan agar
            setiap pengeluaran lebih sadar dan terarah.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mission-card" data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-delay="100" data-aos-duration="900">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 26 26" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <rect x="5" y="3" width="16" height="20" rx="3.5" stroke="#2F4F7F" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" />
              <rect x="8" y="7" width="10" height="7" rx="2" fill="#2F4F7F" opacity="0.10" stroke="#2F4F7F"
                stroke-width="1.2" />
              <circle cx="10" cy="18" r="1.5" fill="#D4A437" />
              <circle cx="13" cy="18" r="1.5" fill="#2F4F7F" opacity="0.3" />
              <circle cx="16" cy="18" r="1.5" fill="#2F4F7F" opacity="0.3" />
              <path d="M9 10.5h8M9 13h5" stroke="#2F4F7F" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.5" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Static Article</h3>
          <p>
            Pelajari strategi menabung dan manajemen bisnis melalui artikel
            yang dirancang untuk membangun kemandirian finansial Anda.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!--=========== CTA Section ============= -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-inner">
      <div class="tag-pill" style="background:  rgba(212,164,55,0.18); color: var(--gold-light)">
        Mulai Sekarang
      </div>
      <h2 style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Saatnya Mengelola Uang<br />dengan Lebih Sadar</h2>
      <p>Bukan hanya mencatat, tetapi memahami dan bertumbuh.</p>
      <a href="register" class="btn-gold">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none">
          <path d="M9 3v8M5 7l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round" />
          <rect x="2" y="13" width="14" height="2.5" rx="1.25" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.3" />
        </svg>
        Coba WiseLedger Gratis
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!--=================== Footer ================ -->
  <footer>
    <p>© 2025 WiseLedger. Capstone project.</p>
    <a href="#">Kebijakan Privasi</a>
  </footer>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

  <script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@next/dist/aos.js"></script>
  <script>
    AOS.init();
  </script>
</body>

</html>